{"tid":2186783,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「疑似」龍心感染性病。大波情婦：唔會離婚！！","createTime":"2020-09-03T07:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T08:02:49.000Z","uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d082e5dd0935c6f42f7ab4709572d924f20bd370","tid":2186783,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"前商台DJ細So偷食一事引起網民熱議，日前事件女主角現真身，就是35歲的人妻兼靚媽KOL練美施Macy。不少人對於Macy有夫之婦的身份感到驚訝，加上她曾傳染性病給老公，又暗示曾為細So墮胎，令不少網民都關注Macy老公的回應。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\nMacy日前在訪問中透露老公已原諒自己，彼此不會離婚。任職中醫的Macy老公王先生今日就接受傳媒訪問，表示支持太太繼續陪在她身邊，更出言護花，形容太太Macy幾乎零缺點堪稱完美，無論是工作抑或照顧家庭都十分稱職：「真係好好，但太易相信人」。 </span><br />\n<br />\n言談之間，王先生透露一早知Macy出軌，指自己在太太與細So開始偷情時，曾與太太商量這段關係，叮囑她不要太相信對方，認為對方並非真心真意。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">試問如果你老公成條柒咁，又似龍心。都唔知係咪早洩虧佬。比我係大波may都會偷食啦，龍心喎！點頂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出面玩到生性病都值啦。雖然有啲錢，最緊要係老公肯接受同埋單，呢啲水魚邊度搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />層樓最緊要寫埋我名，莫講話而家玩到性病，就算玩到肺炎，你都冇得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdkAz66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdkAz66.png&h=a44ec88a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUT6GM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhUT6GM9.png&h=b599f948&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dK9xCkx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdK9xCkx.png&h=fe790420&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPhnZyV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPhnZyV.png&h=ccfd866d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22a454083aa1a5d996d3d2478d73b945457575d6","tid":2186783,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cee761c4c7d30fade10090605daa11bdfb86dbd","tid":21